# Top-level images folder.
#
# Drop og-image.jpg directly into this folder (1200x630 — the Open Graph
# share image referenced by every page's <meta property="og:image">).
#
# Subfolders:
#   hero/      — full-screen hero images (one per page)
#   services/  — service-card backgrounds
#   gallery/   — gallery photographs
#   team/      — team-member portraits
#   logos/     — membership / affiliation logos
